tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE GeneExpression (
  gene_id INT,
  tissue_id INT,
  expression_value FLOAT,
  PRIMARY KEY (gene_id, tissue_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES Genes(gene_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (tissue_id) REFERENCES Tissues(tissue_id)
);

CREATE TABLE GeneExpressionData (
    gene_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_name STRING,
    tissue_type STRING,
    expression_level FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Analysis { 
     analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
     analysis_name VARCHAR(50), 
     gene_id INT, 
     sample_id INT, 
     experiment_id INT 
 }
